ap_Menu.png", "id": "1012519640612356", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974570_1012519647279022_6705925294837175412_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oK7kiw68n0kQ7kNvgEm-P7E&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCN26Tm2VFKO_oVRVNNGxUluE5bXsB96pO6njvScBBlIw&oe=66FBE3A3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "WiVi", "keywords": ["wifi", "networking", "wireless", "analyzer", "scanner"], "long_description": "WiVi is the ultimate AR tool for spatially visualizing and optimizing your WiFi network. Whether you're at home streaming VR games, or engaging in a remote work video meeting, WiVi helps you map and understand your wireless environment with precision.\n\n- **Signal Strength Mapping:** Walk around your space to create a real-time spatial map of your WiFi coverage. Accounts for walls, windows, etc.\n- **Internet Speed & Latency Measurement:** Assess your network\u2019s performance with detailed speed tests and ping analysis.\n- **Interference Detection:** Identify overlapping networks and interference sources to improve your connection quality.\n- **AR-Powered Visualization:** Utilize mixed reality to see your network\u2019s performance through your Meta Quest headset.\n\nWhether you\u2019re a network enthusiast, a professional, or someone just looking to improve their WiFi, WiVi offers the tools you need to optimize your wireless experience.", "short_description": "Explore and map your WiFi like never before with WiVi, the AR-powered tool that visualizes your signal strength, internet speed, and interference in the world around you.\n\nWalk through your home or office to build a detailed map of the space. Ideal for optimizing your wireless setup for streaming games or video meetings."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/wivi-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/wivi-terms-of-service", "publisher_nam